title: #58 - Mizkif Reveals His Worst Fan Encounter & Honest Opinion on Adin Ross
itunes:title: #58 - Mizkif Reveals His Worst Fan Encounter & Honest Opinion on Adin Ross
description: On this previously-livestreamed podcast, CouRage, AustinShow & Will Neff bring on one of the most popular Twitch streamers and their personal friend, Mizkif. They cover a range of topic such as how much money Mizkif's lost opening Pokemon Cards, who he thinks the next addition to OTK should be, thoughts on Adin Ross's success, and more!
